title: G Baby on Getting Shot Doing Graffiti, Getting Put on The Hood & More
description:
G Baby talks about his come-up, family dynamic, losing his teeth, the streets, upcoming music, and more. His main IG got hacked so you can now follow G Baby here: https://www.instagram.com/darealgbaby... ----- 00:00 Intro 0:55 - Growing up Mexican in Pico-Union. Clarifying that he didn’t get his face tattoos to go viral as a rapper 13:55 - Getting ready to put out a new tape with all the homies on it.
